{"id":4087,"date":"2025-06-14T14:29:20","date_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:29:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4087"},"modified":"2025-06-14T14:29:20","modified_gmt":"2025-06-14T07:29:20","slug":"kem-tay-da-chet","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/kem-tay-da-chet\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft? Kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC Natural Peeling"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng <\/span><\/i><a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-tay-da-chet\/\"><b><i>kem t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft<\/i><\/b><\/a><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng trong quy tr\u00ecnh ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ch\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi v\u00ec sao vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho l\u00e0n da? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng an to\u00e0n trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9.<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tay-te-bao-chet-cho-da-la-sao\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da l\u00e0 sao?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da \u0111\u00e3 c\u0169 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da tr\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap c\u00e1c l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. C\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u00edch t\u1ee5, khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb b\u00edt t\u1eafc, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4088\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4088\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4088\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da l\u00e0 sao\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4088\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da l\u00e0 sao<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-can-tay-te-bao-chet-cho-da\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft mang l\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i \u00edch. T\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p da \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a l\u00e0n da:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4089\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4089\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4089\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4089\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7n t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>C\u1ea3i Thi\u1ec7n V\u1ec1 Th\u1ea9m M\u1ef9<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, da c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta lu\u00f4n thay m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang s\u1ebd l\u00e0m da tr\u00f4ng x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 k\u00e9m t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn. T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb ngo\u00e0i r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>T\u0103ng C\u01b0\u1eddng Hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 Ch\u0103m S\u00f3c Da<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: T\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0o s\u00e2u b\u00ean trong. Khi lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><b>Ng\u0103n Ng\u1eeba M\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1. T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft s\u1ebd gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn b\u1edfi d\u1ea7u, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 vi khu\u1ea9n. H\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u0111a nguy c\u01a1 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft c\u00f2n gi\u00fap th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da. L\u00e0m m\u1edd v\u1ebft th\u00e2m v\u00e0 s\u1eb9o hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1edd vi\u1ec7c k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-diem-vang-tay-te-bao-chet-cho-da-mat\"><\/span><b>Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0ng t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft cho da m\u1eb7t?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y T\u1ebf B\u00e0o Ch\u1ebft V\u00e0o Bu\u1ed5i S\u00e1ng: N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y m\u1edbi, h\u00e3y t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da v\u00e0 mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y T\u1ebf B\u00e0o Ch\u1ebft V\u00e0o Bu\u1ed5i T\u1ed1i: T\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0o m\u1ed7i t\u1ed1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf h\u1ebft l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn c\u00f2n s\u00f3t l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean da. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap da s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111i v\u00e0o gi\u1ea5c ng\u1ee7.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u01b0u \u00fd: Kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean nh\u1eefng v\u00f9ng da c\u00f3 v\u1ebft th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u1edf. V\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-natural-peeling-%e2%80%93-kem-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc-an-toan-cho-da\"><\/span><strong>GSC Natural Peeling &#8211; kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc an to\u00e0n cho da<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>GSC Natural Peeling<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n cho l\u00e0n da. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n <\/span><b>Papain<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb m\u1ee7 \u0111u \u0111\u1ee7. Kem gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da ch\u1ebft, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da m\u1edbi. M\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9 pH t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4090\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4090\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4090\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-3.webp\" alt=\"GSC Natural Peeling\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4090\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Natural Peeling<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-kem-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc-gsc\"><\/span><strong>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft: Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n b\u00e1m s\u00e2u trong l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m tho\u00e1ng l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng: T\u1ea9y s\u1ea1ch b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 t\u1eafc ngh\u1ebdn.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t: Sau khi t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da m\u1edbi: Kem gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4092\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4092\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4092\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5.webp\" alt=\"GSC Natural Peeling c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4092\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Natural Peeling c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-noi-bat\"><\/span><strong>Th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ea7n N\u1ed5i B\u1eadt<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Papain &#8211; chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111u \u0111\u1ee7: Gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u1edbi m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u1ea7n t\u00e2y<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i xanh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e0 r\u1ed1t<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eadu n\u00e0nh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ea1t lanh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Qu\u1ea3 c\u00e0 chua<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00f4 h\u1ed9i<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eadu b\u1eafp<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TBG nho<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">TBG hoa sen<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e1 \u0111ay<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4091\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4091\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4091\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-4.webp\" alt=\"Th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ea7n N\u1ed5i B\u1eadt\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/45-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4091\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>Th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ea7n N\u1ed5i B\u1eadt<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u00e0 c\u00f2n cung c\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t thi\u1ebft y\u1ebfu. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0n da, mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng, kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-nghe-tay-da-chet-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng Ngh\u1ec7 T\u1ea9y Da Ch\u1ebft Sinh H\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc v\u1edbi enzym tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y. GSC Natural Peeling gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111au r\u00e1t, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch hay k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ecfng da. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 duy tr\u00ec l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng Hydrolipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"so-sanh-3-phuong-phap-tay-da-chet-vat-ly-hoa-hoc-va-sinh-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">So s\u00e1nh 3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft: V\u1eadt l\u00fd, H\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 Sinh h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da lu\u00f4n m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng. Hi\u1ec7n nay, c\u00f3 ba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn: t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd, t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc v\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc. M\u1ed7i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng ri\u00eang. Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1c nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng so s\u00e1nh chi ti\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft v\u1eadt l\u00fd<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1ea1t scrub, b\u00e0n ch\u1ea3i ho\u1eb7c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid nh\u01b0 AHA, BHA, PHA \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, gi\u00fap da bong tr\u00f3c t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00f9ng enzyme ho\u1eb7c acid t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ec1m v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp l\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, ch\u1ec9 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u00ean l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn da m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng ngay sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; D\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian th\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cao v\u1edbi da d\u1ea7u, m\u1ee5n nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da, gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; D\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; N\u1ebfu h\u1ea1t scrub qu\u00e1 to ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e0 x\u00e1t m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 da th\u00edch nghi.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; Hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ch\u1eadm h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">&#8211; C\u1ea7n ki\u00ean tr\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i da ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da th\u01b0\u1eddng, da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p, da \u00edt nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da d\u1ea7u, da m\u1ee5n, da s\u1ea7n s\u00f9i, c\u00f3 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to.<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da y\u1ebfu, da sau \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb.<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">1-2 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n (t\u00f9y v\u00e0o n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 acid)<\/span><\/td>\n<td><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n<\/span><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft GSC Natural Peeling<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi cho nh\u1eefng ai t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng nh\u01b0ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da tr\u1edf n\u00ean s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1i tr\u1ebb m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng hay l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da. V\u1edbi c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 sau m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd t\u1ef1 h\u1ecfi v\u00ec sao vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch m\u00e0 n\u00f3 mang l\u1ea1i cho l\u00e0n da? H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chi ti\u1ebft kem t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft sinh h\u1ecdc GSC v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng an to\u00e0n trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4093,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4087","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4087","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4087"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4087\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4094,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4087\/revisions\/4094"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4093"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4087"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4087"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=4087"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}